<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />I am forgotten as a dead man whom no one thinks about.</para>

<para style="q1">I am like a broken pot.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />For I have heard the whispering of many,</para>

<para style="q1">terrifying news from every side</para>

<para style="q1">as they plot together against me.</para>

<para style="q1">They plot to take away my life.</para>
